	measure 'Invoiced + Open Amount – Next Month' = ```
			
			VAR StartDate = [NextMonthStart]
			VAR EndDate   = [NextMonthEnd]
			VAR NullDate = DATE(2025,10,1)
			
			VAR MonthDates =
			    FILTER (
			        ALL ( Dim_Date ),
			        Dim_Date[Date] >= StartDate &&
			        Dim_Date[Date] <= EndDate
			    )
			
			VAR ClosedAmtNextMonth =
			    CALCULATE (
			        SUM ( Fact_Sales[Amount] ),
			        Fact_Sales[SalesLine_Status] = "Invoiced",
			        USERELATIONSHIP (
			            Fact_Sales[InvoiceDateKey],
			            Dim_Date[DateKey]
			        ),
			        MonthDates
			    )
			
			VAR OpenAmtNextMonth_ReqShip =
			    CALCULATE (
			        SUM ( Fact_Sales[Amount] ),
			        Fact_Sales[SalesLine_Status] = "Open",
			        USERELATIONSHIP ( Fact_Sales[SalesLine_ShipDateKey], Dim_Date[DateKey] ),
			        FILTER (
			            ALL ( Dim_Date ),
			            Dim_Date[Date] >= StartDate &&
			            Dim_Date[Date] <= EndDate
			        )
			    )
			
			RETURN
			    ClosedAmtNextMonth + OpenAmtNextMonth_ReqShip
			
			```
		lineageTag: 43790719-4309-4e07-9ffa-53d6298e944d

		changedProperty = Name

