	measure 'Invoiced + Open Amount – Selected Period' = ```
			
			VAR StartDate =
			    [BaseMonthStart]
			VAR EndDate =
			    [BaseMonthEnd]
			
			-- Only this month's invoiced amount (by invoice date)
			VAR ClosedAmtSelectedPeriod =
			    CALCULATE (
			        SUM ( Fact_Sales[Amount] ),
			        Fact_Sales[SalesLine_Status] = "Invoiced",
			        USERELATIONSHIP (
			            Fact_Sales[InvoiceDateKey],
			            Dim_Date[DateKey]
			        ),
			        FILTER (
			            ALL ( Dim_Date ),
			            Dim_Date[Date] >= StartDate &&
			            Dim_Date[Date] <= EndDate
			        )
			    )
			
			-- Open amount for all orders with requested ship date up to *end* of month
			VAR OpenAmtUpToPeriod_ReqShip =
			    CALCULATE (
			        SUM ( Fact_Sales[Amount] ),
			        Fact_Sales[SalesLine_Status] = "Open",
			        USERELATIONSHIP (
			            Fact_Sales[SalesLine_ShipDateKey],
			            Dim_Date[DateKey]
			        ),
			        FILTER (
			            ALL ( Dim_Date ),
			            Dim_Date[Date] <= EndDate        -- cumulative up to the end of the selected month
			        )
			    )
			
			RETURN
			    ClosedAmtSelectedPeriod + OpenAmtUpToPeriod_ReqShip
			
			```
		lineageTag: b298a6ed-027f-4f6c-9a4e-a3176d0d30ef

